column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian, ife.ra as ifeRA, ife.dec as ifeDEC, e.bpt, e.Flux_Ha_#, e.Flux_Ha_#_Err, e.EW_Ha_#, e.EW_Ha_#_Err, e.Flux_NII_#, e.Flux_NII_#_err into mydb.ife_whan_dr1# from mydb.for_bpt as ife CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq (ife.ra, ife.dec, #) AS near JOIN SpecObjAll as s ON near.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specObjID = near.specObjID WHERE s.class = # AND s.zWarning = # AND e.Flux_Ha_# ! = # AND e.Flux_NII_# ! = # AND s.snMedian > = #
